@startuml
class User
class Admin
class System
Class Moderator
class Dashboard
class Software
class Hardware
class Network
class Notification
class Router
class SistemaAlarmas
class SistemaIncendios
class SecurityCamera


Admin -r-- System
Admin <|-- Notification
Admin --- User
Admin -- Moderator

Moderator -- User
Moderator -- Dashboard

User .r.. Dashboard

System --- Dashboard
System *-- Notification

Dashboard -- Software
Dashboard -- Hardware

Software -- SistemaAlarmas
Software -- SistemaIncendios
Software -- Network

Hardware -- SecurityCamera
Hardware -- Router
Hardware -- Switch




@enduml
